                    <head xml:lang="en">Collect and organize metadata</head>
                    <head xml:lang="fr">Collecter et organiser les métadonnées.</head>
                    <desc xml:lang="en" type="definition">Add metadata according to Dublin Core
                        standard. Create a structured database about people, places, sources, etc.
                        related to the musical edition conforming to Dublin Core standards and
                        organised through the Omeka CMS web publishing system.</desc>
